{"tid":237654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"道德撚開始講唔掂道德，轉講人性","createTime":"2017-05-10T13:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T18:28:54.000Z","uid":33307,"like":13,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de2ff94cd754b58d6a4c6529d972563c9a169d97","tid":237654,"uid":33307,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:41:35.000Z","msg":"有道德有人性唔係問題<br />\n<br />\n大部分道德撚既問題係<br />\n佢地瘋狂對身邊一同身處水深火熱既人口誅筆伐<br />\n但係對住真真正正每日打壓市民既人就有無限大愛<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n道德撚日日屌柒得把口網上兇狠既連登仔（明明係網上講下）<br />\n但係對住暴政（實實在在）黑警，又話要理性，大和解<br />\n<br />\n講到尾呢班人就係欺善怕惡<br />\n有日黑警搵把槍指住佢個頭，佢又可以放棄佢d道德人性"},{"pid":"ece1b65b5222857c688ce0291014c29426c97d55","tid":237654,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fda9c557324794d6601033a203cb40b208e0614","tid":237654,"uid":41382,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:43:31.000Z","msg":"啲道德撚想等自己個心舒服啲嘛，由佢地囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a324aab5e1ccf0e24bdc6cad61c1f123ffc193ff","tid":237654,"uid":33307,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:45:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲道德撚想等自己個心舒服啲嘛，由佢地囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n道德撚害死香港好多次<br />\n例子：928，光復"},{"pid":"de52d83871b80f5e5b920b027fabd059568e1b32","tid":237654,"uid":33307,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:48:27.000Z","msg":"再比多個例子：<br />\n最近好多人屌網上吹水既冇女毒撚連登仔，有邊個屌柒個實實在在既強姦犯？"},{"pid":"f8a792c9174f4b29fad26aec2f09e285f1f0d0b7","tid":237654,"uid":62494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"班大愛左膠淨係識選擇性道德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63f15a6d5d1680cee7ab3f43af6c82870ffdd38","tid":237654,"uid":33307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05