,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:32:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>班大愛左膠淨係識選擇性道德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢位巴打心水清<br />\n再直接d：<br />\n佢地係對住弱者講道德</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n左膠淨係識叫我地大愛包容蝻同支那人<br />\n之前有個女仔係公園俾蝻姦左 又唔見班偽道德撚出黎<br />\n因為知道蝻亞人好打夠癲 班友就唔敢出聲"},{"pid":"ce83b50963509d4240baf997bec2713f06f4cdfc","tid":237654,"uid":95623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:33:58.000Z","msg":"關咩道德撚事 明明就係成班連登仔自以為是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 花生友"},{"pid":"95e23bcd695fb443ed1f330e343469bd9e8dbb20","tid":237654,"uid":33307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:34:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>網上鳩up幾句班口德道德撚就起晒鋼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2953837f0ae564498fefb958173c6ac7e4d5b0db","tid":237654,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:52:01.000Z","msg":"佢地要用連登仔個朵黎溝女，唔勤力D洗地又畀囡囡笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0bd8e0a27b685c6e794ed17ac2b91cc168c133","tid":237654,"uid":89282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T18:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲道德撚想等自己個心舒服啲嘛，由佢地囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係，btw口德撚呢個名唔差，攞黎做鳩膠幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}